<p>Enter the percentage value or flat rate value. The choice depends on the payment provider and the conditions of your contract.<br>
<strong>Important</strong>: Do not enter a value into both fields. For example, if for the payment method <strong>Cash on delivery</strong> you enter the value 4.00 into the field <strong>Domestic (surcharge): Flat rate</strong>, then the customer will have to pay a 4.00 EUR surcharge when selecting cash on delivery. If you enter the value 4.00 into the field <strong>Domestic (surcharge): Percentage</strong>, then a 4% surcharge will be calculated.</p>
