<div class="paragraph">
<p>You have to configure additional settings beyond those listed in the table for <a href="/en/order-processing/payment">payment methods</a> that require you to work with a payment provider (e.g. PayPal, Sofortbanking, wirecard etc.). For these payment methods, your online store will later transfer a payment request to the payment provider and receive a confirmation after the payment has been made.</p>
</div>
