</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Your online store will be displayed with a fully functional test design. You can change the design and add to it according to your needs. To do so, select one of the default designs available in the <a href="/en/omni-channel/online-store/cms">CMS</a> menu. If you want to have a highly customised design, you can work with one of our <a href="https://www.plentymarkets.eu/partner/zertifizierte-agenturen/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">certified service providers</a>.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>This guide provides explanations for working with the default design and focuses primarily on inserting texts, images and links. At minimum, you will need to have a <strong>homepage</strong> and additional pages containing <strong>contact</strong> and <strong>shipping</strong> information as well as a <strong>legal disclosure</strong> and a <strong>privacy policy</strong>. You are not legally required to have a page of <strong>terms and conditions</strong>, but we strongly recommend that you do so because of the security that it provides.</p>
</div>
