<td class="content">
<div class="title">Tip: Automating the import of package numbers</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>There are several different ways to import package numbers into plentymarkets: You can fill out forms much quicker with the help of a USB scanner. If you process a large number of shipments, then we recommend that you import these entries from your shipping software into the system.</p>
</div>
</td>
