</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>When package numbers are imported, this next <a href="/en/basics/automation/event-procedures">event procedure</a> sends a shipping confirmation, changes the order status to 7 and books the outgoing items from the warehouse, thus updating the physical stock.</p>
