<div class="paragraph">
<p>Nowadays, nearly all shipping service providers allow customers to track packages online. You already saved a tracking URL while setting up your shipping service providers. Once the package number has been entered, your plentymarkets system has all of the necessary information to send customers a tracking URL for their package. Use this option and make sure that the shipping confirmation email contains the variable <strong>$TrackingURL</strong>. You should also test the first tracking URLs yourself to ensure that they have been processed correctly and that the customer has all the information.</p>
</div>
