<div class="paragraph">
<p>If your customer fails to pay despite the payment reminder, then create another email template that is more strongly worded, e.g. a payment request. Create a new procedure for the second dunning level and use it to send the template. Filter all of the unpaid invoices, i.e. orders that are in <strong>status 3</strong>. Select a longer period of time in the <strong>Last status change</strong> field (e.g. 20 days).</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Your last option for dealing with unpaid invoices is to hand the orders over to a <a href="/en/order-processing/payment">collection agency</a>. plentymarkets also offers a simple solution for taking care of this automatically.</p>
</div>
</div>
